# SSOT documentation and milestone closure

## Non-negotiable closure (same change set as substantive work)

**New Agent / IDE restart:** operators may paste only **[`docs/NEW_CHAT_SINGLE_FILE_HANDOFF_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/NEW_CHAT_SINGLE_FILE_HANDOFF_SSOT.md)** — it already links the playbook, hooks, MCP verify, and gateway notes.

When a slice is **merge-ready**, agents and operators follow **[`docs/CONTINUE_ENGINEERING_PLAYBOOK_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/CONTINUE_ENGINEERING_PLAYBOOK_SSOT.md)** sections **5.1 through 5.4** (and **§0** when the operator sends only **continue**—update the **Continue queue** in [`COMPREHENSIVE_PROJECT_STATUS_REPORT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/COMPREHENSIVE_PROJECT_STATUS_REPORT.md) in the **same** change set when priorities or blockers move):

1. **Git** — **`git commit`** + **`git push`** (and consumer pins when required) per **§3a** / §5.1 — not “saved files only.”
2. **Consolidation** — prefer **extending** canonical SSOT ([`00_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/00_SSOT.md)); scan [`REPOSITORY_RESTRUCTURING_DOC_CONSOLIDATION_2026-04-27.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/REPOSITORY_RESTRUCTURING_DOC_CONSOLIDATION_2026-04-27.md) for tranche rules; **no** new parallel master docs without supersedes/links.
3. **Cross-references** — update **Quick Nav** / indexes; fix internal links; run **`scripts/verify-ssot-dashboards.sh`** when dashboards touched; run **`scripts/verify-ssot-program-operating-docs.sh`** when **`PROGRAM_*`** checkout/deploy docs, **`sync-program-checkouts.sh`**, **`reusable-mandatory-predeploy`**, or **`config/local-runner-scripts.manifest.txt`** / listed **`scripts/*.sh`** change (**`./scripts/update-local-runner-scripts-hashes.sh`** when edits touch manifest paths — [MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md) **§1f**). **MCP / Cloudflare verify procedures:** extend **[`docs/MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md)** instead of pasting multi-step commands into **COMPREHENSIVE**, canvas narrative, or duplicate playbooks. **Do not** add **`docs/handoff/*`** “delta stub” markdown that only points at **COMPREHENSIVE**—extend **[`COMPREHENSIVE_PROJECT_STATUS_REPORT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/COMPREHENSIVE_PROJECT_STATUS_REPORT.md)** and the consolidation **[`REPOSITORY_RESTRUCTURING_DOC_CONSOLIDATION_2026-04-27.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/REPOSITORY_RESTRUCTURING_DOC_CONSOLIDATION_2026-04-27.md)** section **7** row instead.
4. **Canvas** — refresh **[`MASTER_PROGRAM_CANVAS_COMPANION_2026-04-27.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/MASTER_PROGRAM_CANVAS_COMPANION_2026-04-27.md)** when program/canvas **content** moves; remind to **close/reopen** the IDE canvas tab if stale.
5. **CHANGELOG** — **`docs/CHANGELOG.md`** for operator-visible changes.
6. **Cursor upgrades** — §5.4: skim [Cursor Changelog](https://cursor.com/changelog); MCP/hooks/smoke verification after installs.
7. **Ephemeral agent summaries** — [`CONTINUE_ENGINEERING_PLAYBOOK_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/CONTINUE_ENGINEERING_PLAYBOOK_SSOT.md) **§7.1**: agents list autonomous follow-up first; surface **operator** only for **human-only** blockers **needed in that same run**. Do **not** use generic **“notify the operator every time”** checklists—SSOT **`COMPREHENSIVE_*`** already tracks **Outstanding token / secret requests** and the **Continue queue**.

## Program documentation wiki (MCP retrieval)

- **Git** `docs/` and **`.cursor/rules/`** are the **only** merge authority and CI contract. The **Centex Program Wiki** (`llm-wiki` / **`centex-program-wiki` MCP`) is a **queryable rendered layer** — see [`WIKI_MIGRATION_AND_AGENT_CONTEXT_OPTIMIZATION_PLAN_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/WIKI_MIGRATION_AND_AGENT_CONTEXT_OPTIMIZATION_PLAN_SSOT.md) (**§4a** slug map, **§4c** prompts, **§4d** enforcement) and [`AGENT_DOCUMENTATION_ROUTING_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/AGENT_DOCUMENTATION_ROUTING_SSOT.md) **§1a** (wiki-first WIP / **Continue queue** context). **`config/prompt-context-routing-matrix.json`** (**`task_class`** → required git parents) must stay aligned with **§4a** wiki slugs for measured prompt-context loads — same doc **§5a** (three-layer contract: Cursor rules + matrix + wiki).
- **Do not** replace `docs/` bodies with mass **`wiki://`** URIs; **do** prefer wiki MCP for **large excerpt** retrieval when configured (reduces prompt stuffing). Policy closure for Phases **3–4** is documented in the wiki plan (same repo).
- **Ongoing:** new or renamed **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** → extend wiki plan **§4a** in the **same** change set. When a rule governs **GitHub Actions** / Workers CI / tokens (for example **`token-governance-enforcement.mdc`**), expand YAML **`description`** with CI vocabulary per [wiki/README.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/wiki/README.md) **§5c** and mirror **`config/cursor-program/rules/`** (**`verify-cursor-program-pack-parity.sh`**). New **Cloudflare API token** operator scenarios in git **`docs/`** → extend [TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md) with a **named token block** (**human-readable steps** + **`CF-` = Cloudflare name = 1Password title** + **Operator mint request** table: **token name**, **exact scopes**, **program values** per **Mint request discipline** on that page) per [wiki/README.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/wiki/README.md) **§5c** so **`token/token-creation-checklist`** ingests a verbatim agent packet. Optional **`WIKI_OPERATING_HEALTHCHECK_ENFORCE=1`** on [`scripts/verify-ssot-program-operating-docs.sh`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/scripts/verify-ssot-program-operating-docs.sh) per plan **§4d** and [`MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md) **§1d**.
- **Wiki compliance (one doc set):** plan **§4h** (tiers A/B/C, forbidden **`wiki://`** bodies); **`reusable-mandatory-predeploy`** input **`wiki-strict-frontmatter`** (**default false**) exports **`WIKI_STRICT_FRONTMATTER_ENFORCE=1`** on **`verify-ssot-program-operating-docs.sh`** when callers opt in — driver **`mandatory-predeploy-gates.yml`** passes **`true`** (**`wiki-program-ssot-sync validate --strict-frontmatter`**).
- **Primary agent retrieval:** when **centex-program-wiki** MCP is enabled, agents treat it as the **primary** read path for **large** SSOT excerpts in chat; **git** edits remain in **`docs/`** + **`.cursor/rules/`** only — plan **§4e**; after substantive doc/rule merges run wiki **re-ingest** per [wiki/README.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/wiki/README.md) **§5a**. CI runs [`scripts/wiki-primary-retrieval-gate.sh`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/scripts/wiki-primary-retrieval-gate.sh) from [`verify-ssot-program-operating-docs.sh`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/scripts/verify-ssot-program-operating-docs.sh); use **`WIKI_PRIMARY_RETRIEVAL_ENFORCE=1`** for strict **`llm-wiki`** healthcheck on trusted hosts.
- **Zero Trust vs wiki-only work:** [wiki/README.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/wiki/README.md) **§5** + [`AGENTS.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/AGENTS.md) + [`00_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/00_SSOT.md) **Agent task routing** — **Continue queue** + **Cloudflare Access (Entra SCIM)** stay anchored in git ([`COMPREHENSIVE_PROJECT_STATUS_REPORT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/COMPREHENSIVE_PROJECT_STATUS_REPORT.md) **Purpose**, [`CLOUDFLARE_ACCESS_IMPLEMENTATION.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/CLOUDFLARE_ACCESS_IMPLEMENTATION.md), plan **§4e.2**, hub **§1e**); [`wiki-primary-retrieval-gate`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/crates/wiki-primary-retrieval-gate/README.md) CI-checks **`AGENTS.md`** + **`00_SSOT.md`** for the §5 contract substrings.
- **Post-milestone gap analysis:** after merge-ready slices that change **Worker** **deploy** / **bootstrap** / **wiki** routing, extend [`WIKI_MIGRATION_AND_AGENT_CONTEXT_OPTIMIZATION_PLAN_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/WIKI_MIGRATION_AND_AGENT_CONTEXT_OPTIMIZATION_PLAN_SSOT.md) **§4e.2** in the same change set when feasible; see [`AGENT_DOCUMENTATION_ROUTING_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/AGENT_DOCUMENTATION_ROUTING_SSOT.md) **§1a** steps **5–6** and [`MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md) **§1d** / **§1g** (post-milestone retrospectives + **MCP roster audit** after **`mcp.json`** / Cursor upgrades).
- **Subset workstation index:** local **`llm-wiki`** may omit some **`docs/*.md`** pages until full-tree **`ingest`** — if **`wiki_search`** / **`wiki_content_read`** misses a file, load **`docs/`** from git ([`WIKI_MIGRATION_AND_AGENT_CONTEXT_OPTIMIZATION_PLAN_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/WIKI_MIGRATION_AND_AGENT_CONTEXT_OPTIMIZATION_PLAN_SSOT.md) **§4e.1 G-11**, [`AGENT_DOCUMENTATION_ROUTING_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/AGENT_DOCUMENTATION_ROUTING_SSOT.md) **§1a**).
- **Cursor `mcp.json`:** use [`scripts/merge-cursor-mcp-wiki-centex.sh`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/scripts/merge-cursor-mcp-wiki-centex.sh) so **`centex-program-wiki`** **`args`** include **`serve --config <abs> --wiki …`** (Agent mount parity with CLI); if Agent **`wiki_spaces_list`** is empty, re-merge + restart Cursor — [wiki/README.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/wiki/README.md) **§4b**.
- **Wiki MCP triage:** if **`wiki_search`** returns a slug but **`wiki_content_read`** fails, use **`wiki_resolve`** — **`exists: false`** ⇒ index ahead of ingested files; **re-ingest** + **`index rebuild`** or read git **`docs/`** ([wiki/README.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/wiki/README.md) **§5a**, plan **§4e.1 G-11**).
- **Structural migration (single source, no mirror copies):** [`WIKI_PRIMARY_STRUCTURAL_MIGRATION_PLAN_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/WIKI_PRIMARY_STRUCTURAL_MIGRATION_PLAN_SSOT.md); **`cargo run -p wiki-program-ssot-sync -- validate`** (wired through [`scripts/verify-ssot-program-operating-docs.sh`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/scripts/verify-ssot-program-operating-docs.sh)); git-only paths [`config/wiki-git-only-ingest-exclude.txt`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/config/wiki-git-only-ingest-exclude.txt); operator Phase 2 [`wiki/PHASE2_SINGLE_SOURCE_OPERATOR_RUNBOOK.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/wiki/PHASE2_SINGLE_SOURCE_OPERATOR_RUNBOOK.md) + pre-flight [`scripts/wiki-structural-phase2-checklist.sh`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/scripts/wiki-structural-phase2-checklist.sh).
- **GitHub Actions / hosted minutes:** **`reusable-mandatory-predeploy`** **`ssot-program-operating-docs`** may **`cargo install`** **`llm-wiki-engine`** + bootstrap when **`wiki-live-ssot`** is **true**; org/repo **Variable** **`DISABLE_WIKI_LIVE_SSOT=1`** skips **`llm-wiki`** on GitHub-hosted runners — [`WIKI_MIGRATION_AND_AGENT_CONTEXT_OPTIMIZATION_PLAN_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/WIKI_MIGRATION_AND_AGENT_CONTEXT_OPTIMIZATION_PLAN_SSOT.md) **§4f**, [`GITHUB_ACTIONS_USAGE_AND_OFFLOAD_AUDIT_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/GITHUB_ACTIONS_USAGE_AND_OFFLOAD_AUDIT_SSOT.md) **§0.1**, [`TRUSTED_MACHINE_AND_CI_AUDIT_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/TRUSTED_MACHINE_AND_CI_AUDIT_SSOT.md) **§1**, [`MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md) **§6**.

